name: Stunted Gestures
description: By Travis LeRoy Southworth | @travisleroy | “Stunted Gestures” (2021), 1700 x 2000px, MP4, 7 second loop. This animated digital painting is part of my series "Thresholds" where I create works partly through a GAN and my own computerized brush strokes. I use the word 'threshold' for my series as it can be a boundary or a starting point of an experience.
